014|accessdate=17 October 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015133450/http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/november/07/the-great-dane|archivedate=15 October 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n*{{soccerway|lasse-vigen-christensen/155066|Lasse Vigen Christensen}}\n*[http://www.dbu.dk/landshold/landsholdsdatabasen/PlayerInfo/6770 Danish national team profile]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20170306212029/http://www.fulhamfc.com/player-profiles/lasse-vigen-christensen Fulham F.C. profile]\n\n{{Br\u00f8ndby IF squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Christensen, Lasse Vigen}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Esbjerg]]\n[[Category:Danish footballers]]\n[[Category:Danish expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Fulham F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Esbjerg fB players]]\n[[Category:FC Midtjylland players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Denmark youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Denmark under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Danish expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Burton Albion F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Br\u00f8ndby IF players]]\n", "name_user": "Nardog", "label": "safe", "comment": "fixingDanish IPA", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lasse_Vigen_Christensen"}
