ptonshire]]\n|19,307\n|7.9\n|12.7\n|-\n| [[M48 motorway|M48]]\n| The [[Severn Bridge]], linking the [[M4 motorway|M4]] at [[Olveston]] (near [[Thornbury, South Gloucestershire|Thornbury]]), over the [[River Severn]], to the [[M4 motorway|M4]] at [[Rogiet]] (near [[Caldicot, Monmouthshire|Caldicot]]).  This used to be part of the [[M4 motorway|M4]] before the [[Second Severn Crossing]] was built.\n| [[Gloucestershire]], [[Monmouthshire]]\n|22,376\n|12\n|19\n|-\n| [[M49 motorway|M49]]\n| A short link from the [[M5 motorway|M5]] to the [[M4 motorway|M4]] west of [[Bristol]].\n| [[Bristol]], [[Gloucestershire]]\n|22,209\n|5.0\n|8.0\n|-\n| [[M50 motorway (Great Britain)|M50]]\n| Linking the [[M5 motorway|M5]] north of [[Tewkesbury]] to [[Ross-on-Wye]].\n| [[Worcestershire]], [[Gloucestershire]], [[Herefordshire]]\n|32,207\n|21.6\n|34.8\n|-\n| [[M53 motorway|M53]]\n| Linking [[Wallasey]] and [[Chester, Cheshire|Chester]].\n| [[Merseyside]], [[Cheshire]]\n|77,578\n|18.9\n|30.4\n|-\n| [[M54 motorway|M54]]\n| Linking the [[M6 motorway|M6]] north of [[Wolverhampton]] to [[Wellington, Shropshire|Wellington]] west of [[Telford]].\n| [[Staffordshire]], [[Shropshire]]\n|67,041\n|23.0\n|37.0\n|-\n| [[M55 motorway|M55]]\n| Linking the [[M6 motorway|M6]] north of [[Preston, Lancashire|Preston]] to [[Blackpool]].\n| [[Lancashire]]\n|82,417\n|12.2\n|19.6\n|-\n| [[M56 motorway|M56]]\n| Linking [[Manchester]] ([[Gatley]]) to the A5117 between [[Ellesmere Port]] and [[Chester, England|Chester]].\n| [[Greater Manchester]], [[Cheshire]]\n|163,045\n|33.3\n|53.6\n|-\n| [[M57 motorway|M57]]\n| The [[Liverpool]] bypass running north-west from the [[M62 motorway|M62]] near [[Huyton]] to [[Switch Island]] between [[Maghull]] and [[Aintree]].\n| [[Merseyside]]\n|98,339\n|10\n|16\n|-\n| [[M58 motorway|M58]]\n| Linking [[Switch Island]] (between [[Maghull]] and [[Aintree]], northern [[Liverpool]]) to [[Orrell, Greater Manchester|Orrell]], near [[Wigan]].\n| [[Merseyside]], [[Lancashire]], [[Greater